What the project is: The project is an implementation of a frontend design of a QR-Code.
 Built with:
    -HTML
    -CSS
 Live Site: https://yarnileach2005-code.github.io/qr-code-frontend-mentor/

What I learned:
    -In this Project I relearned the basic elements of html and css.
    -how to position singular elements in a container
    -when to use Grids, Flexbox, or normal positioning
    -how to work with variables and naming conventions
    -how to work with Figma
What I would do differently:
    -better structuring of css

The Project brief of the task can be found here: https://www.frontendmentor.io/challenges/qr-code-component-iux_sIO_H




